{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Require Property Management agents to disclose all Service Charge Accounts",
        "additional_details": "I believe this is necessary to ensure service charge discounts cannot be offered to leaseholders who may have a financial interest with the managing agents and freeholders. I think it is critical that this information is made public to ensure full accountability to all leaseholders within the estate.",
        "background": "I think property management agents should be required to disclose the service charge accounts for all leaseholders contributing to the overall management costs of a property estate. I think this disclosure is necessary to ensure transparency and prevent misconduct.",
